		<p>
			Hi, my name is Cha Chi, pronunciation cha-chee. I am 6 years old; my favorite person is my Human. She rescued me from the snowy winter day one day six years ago. Some of my favorite things are playing fetch, which is so much fun. I also love to lie in the window and watch all the birds and squirrels. I get so excited to see them. Sometimes I even talk to them.
