	<h2>Looks</h2>
		<img src= "images/chachi9.jpg" alt="Chachi look"/>
		<p>
			Their most striking feature is their gorgeous coat. Itâ€™s a double coat that is short, plush, and velvety soft. The color of the outer coat is lilac at the base and tipped with silver, giving the Russian Blue a shimmering appearance.
		</p>
		<p>
			The eyes are round and bright emerald green in adult cats. They have a stunning effect set off by the blue of their fur. Kittens will have yellow eyes that darken to green as they grow.
		</P>
		
	<h2>Personality</h2>
		
		<video autoplay muted>
			<source src="chachi5.mp4" type="video/mp4">
