		<p>
			Russian Blues are content to entertain themselves if, no one is home during the day. But Russian Blue's will be happy to see you when you arrive home. This cat makes for an excellent companion, constantly following its human around. They do generally prefer one human above all others in the family. 
		</p>
		<p>
			They are talkative (but soft-spoken). Russian Blue humans say; they love to engage in back-and-forth conversations with them. That is one of the reasons why they make for a great company.
		</p>
		<p>
			Russian blue cats are highly intelligent cats. They do require physical and mental stimulation. Their humans say it is important to give them access to toys at all times. They retain a strong hunting instinct, so a feathered fishing pole toy is the perfect plaything. 
		</P>
